    java.io.Serializable, nl.tudelft.simulation.event.EventProducerInterface

    public abstract class CoupledModel
extends AbstractDEVSPortModel
    CoupledModel class. This class implements the classic parallel DEVS coupled model with ports conform Zeigler et al. (2000), section 4.3.
